name: Grain_Wood_Furniture_Valerie_Solid_Wood_Bench
reviews: I bought two benches to match our table and it looks lovely! Recommend!
the bench goes good with the table
I was a little disappointed that there was so much white mixed. It works, but if you don't want a lot of white reconsider.
Great quality wood. Easy to put together, unbelievable price. My suggestion is go for it!
Again, great quality. Easy to assemble. Looks great with table, great for kids, entertaining. Color is beautiful.
This is very cute, love the look of it. There are some imperfections but it adds to the charm.
